<h1>Booking Cancellation</h1>

<p>Dear <%= @customer.name %>,</p>

<p>Your booking for <strong><%= @event.title %></strong> has been successfully cancelled.</p>

<h2>Cancelled Booking Details:</h2>
<ul>
  <li><strong>Event:</strong> <%= @event.title %></li>
  <li><strong>Date:</strong> <%= @event.event_date.strftime('%B %d, %Y at %I:%M %p') %></li>
  <li><strong>Venue:</strong> <%= @event.venue %></li>
  <li><strong>Ticket Type:</strong> <%= @ticket.ticket_type %></li>
  <li><strong>Quantity:</strong> <%= @booking.quantity %></li>
  <li><strong>Total Price:</strong> $<%= sprintf('%.2f', @booking.total_price) %></li>
  <li><strong>Booking Reference:</strong> #<%= @booking.id %></li>
</ul>

<p>If you paid for this booking, a refund will be processed according to our refund policy.</p>

<p>If you have any questions about your cancellation or refund, please contact our customer support team.</p>

<p>Best regards,<br>The Event Booking Team</p>
